[I] Multipath-tools for Linux

[T] This package provides the programs to drive the Device Mapper multipathing
[T] driver: multipath: Device mapper target autoconfig. multipathc: Interactive
[T] client for multipathd. multipathd: Multipath daemon. mpathpersist:
[T] Manages SCSI persistent reservations on dm multipath devices. kpartx:
[T] Create device maps from partition tables.


[U] https://github.com/opensvc/multipath-tools

[A] opensvc
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS

